  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/597150/extras/88d826aa67e917ef44697a7c1f53f1c1.poster.avif?t=1725191245\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/597150/extras/88d826aa67e917ef44697a7c1f53f1c1.webm?t=1725191245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/597150/extras/88d826aa67e917ef44697a7c1f53f1c1.mp4?t=1725191245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Raise your army, learn powerful combos and take back your land!</strong><br><br><strong>Slash</strong> and <strong>Dash</strong> your way through hundreds of enemies in the fast-paced skill-based action of <strong>Hyper Knights!</strong><br><br>Become stronger and learn new powerful <strong>combos</strong> to help you on your journey.<br><br>Raise your army and recruit allied Knights to join your cause, command their armies, <strong>siege</strong> enemy castles, <strong>raid</strong> their outposts, <strong>ambush</strong> their convoys and use the <strong>loot</strong> to build your lands.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/597150/extras/e6aad0070e8f5f3d2f7cbf3372617f11.poster.avif?t=1725191245\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/597150/extras/e6aad0070e8f5f3d2f7cbf3372617f11.webm?t=1725191245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/597150/extras/e6aad0070e8f5f3d2f7cbf3372617f11.mp4?t=1725191245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li><strong>Slash</strong> and <strong>Dash</strong> through your enemies<br>    </li><l